name: Geiru Toneido - Ace Attorney
description:
My prompt tests were quickly done. Better people than I can probably get better results.

A character from the game Ace Attorney (never played it). Her design has interested me for a while.

Trying to see what TI can do! This one turned out great! I didn't know how it would handle the nose. 🤡
